subs.text: Knicks fans, in our hearts, don't believe wins like tonight's are actually possible, but the Knicks crushed the Cavs to go up 2-1 in the series. Do we dare dream of more? It wasn't that long ago that we were wearing paper bags over our heads.

I asked ChatGPT for a list of famous rock songs chosen at random in the form of an HTML unordered list. I needed a bit of test code I was working on. Another use-case: Making programming a bit more fun.
